/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯已批准军队现代化的第三阶段，其中包括购买该国第一艘潜艇，以捍卫其在有争议的南中国海的海洋主权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-plans-buy-submarines-defend-sovereignty-south-china-sea-senior-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车将停止资助 Polestar，可能将股份转让给吉利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-volvo-cars-stop-funding-polestar-quarterly-earnings-above-estimates-2024-02-01/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周四表示，将停止向北极星汽车控股公司提供资金，并将这个陷入困境的豪华汽车品牌的责任移交给沃尔沃最大股东中国吉利控股公司。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 06:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-volvo-cars-stop-funding-polestar-quarterly-earnings-above-estimates-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：对于市场来说，美联储推迟五月意味着更多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-01/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 05:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>人权观察就中国强迫劳动风险向汽车制造商发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/human-rights-watch-warns-carmakers-over-china-forced-labour-risk-2024-02-01/</link><description>人权观察敦促特斯拉、大众和比亚迪等汽车制造商采取更多措施，确保可能使用维吾尔族强迫劳动制造的材料不会进入其供应链。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 05:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/human-rights-watch-warns-carmakers-over-china-forced-labour-risk-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院以2019年冲击立法会后骚乱罪判处四人有罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-convicts-four-rioting-after-2019-legislature-storming-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四，香港一家法院认定四人犯有 2019 年民主抗议活动期间金融中心立法机关遭到冲击后发生的骚乱罪，另外八人也承认了对该事件的指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-convicts-four-rioting-after-2019-legislature-storming-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软，亚洲工厂举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asias-factories-struggle-momentum-amid-soft-chinese-demand-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四的调查显示，亚洲工厂 1 月份的表现基本参差不齐，因为中国需求疲软导致该地区经济在 2024 年初基础不稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:02:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asias-factories-struggle-momentum-amid-soft-chinese-demand-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺坚持财政扩张以刺激经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-growth-picks-up-2023-2024-02-01/</link><description>财政部副部长王东伟周四表示，中国今年将维持财政扩张，以刺激经济复苏，这强化了市场观点，即公共支出将是政府拉动经济增长的主要工具。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 03:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-growth-picks-up-2023-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉中国对部分 Model Y 车型提供现金折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-china-offers-cash-discounts-some-model-y-types-2024-02-01/</link><description>特斯拉中国在其官方社交媒体账户上表示，从周四开始，特斯拉中国将针对部分型号的 Model Y 车辆提供 8,000 元人民币（1,114 美元）的现金折扣。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 02:54:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-china-offers-cash-discounts-some-model-y-types-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国新建住宅价格涨幅为近2-1/2年来最快——私人调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-jan-new-home-prices-rise-fastest-pace-since-aug-2021-private-survey-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四发布的一项调查显示，在政府出台一系列支持措施以及购房政策进一步放松的预期之后，中国1月份新建住宅价格涨幅为近2-1/2年来最快。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 02:39:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-jan-new-home-prices-rise-fastest-pace-since-aug-2021-private-survey-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>受降息预期提振油价小幅走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-up-us-fed-rate-signals-china-property-sector-support-2024-02-01/</link><description>受美联储可能开始降息的信号以及中国针对陷入困境的房地产市场推出新的支持措施的支撑，油价周四小幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 02:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-up-us-fed-rate-signals-china-property-sector-support-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>美元逼近七周高位，因三月美联储降息押注有所减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-7-week-high-fed-cut-bets-shift-may-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四，美元兑欧元汇率维持在七周高点附近，这是在美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔推翻美国最早在三月份降息的想法后达到的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:57:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-7-week-high-fed-cut-bets-shift-may-2024-02-01/</guid></item><item><title>出口订单推动中国工厂活动扩大——财新PMI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-export-order-boost-caixin-pmi-2024-02-01/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于产量稳定增长、物流加快以及新出口订单自 6 月以来首次增加，中国 1 月份工厂活动有所扩大，帮助将商业信心提升至九个月高点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:53:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-export-order-boost-caixin-pmi-2024-02-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>